This is Palantir, a portable VNC client. It uses the SDL and SDL_net libraries for portable graphics, input, and network access, and has been tested on Mac OS X and x86 Linux.

Docs are sparse right now. Source code documentation is available via Doxygen. Type "make docs" to generate HTML technical docs.

This software is released under Overcode's Source License (http://www.overcode.net/~overcode/osl.txt).
